allProposalTotalVotes().details: Accessor to the internal vote counts for a given proposal.

cancel().details: Cancels the contest. Emits a {IGovernor-ContestCanceled} event.

comment(uint256,string).details: Comment on a proposal. Emits a {CommentCreated} event.

contestAddressTotalVotesCast(address).details: Accessor to how many votes an address has cast total for the contest so far.

contestDeadline().details: Timestamp the contest vote ends. Votes close at the end of this block, so it is not possible to vote in a block with a timestamp after this.

currentPricePerVote().details: Returns the current cost per vote.

getAllAddressesThatHaveVoted().details: Return all addresses that have voted.

getAllAuthorsOfDeletedProposals().details: Return all authors of deleted proposals.

getNumProposalsWithThisManyVotes(uint256.details: Get the number of proposals that have a given number of votes.

getOnlyProposalIdWithThisManyVotes(uint2.details: Get the only proposal id with this many votes. NOTE: Should only get called at a point at which you are sure there is only one proposal id       with a certain number of votes (we only use it in the RewardsModule after ties have       been checked for).

getProposalComments(uint256).details: Return the array of commentIds on a given proposalId.

getProposalsWithThisManyVotes(uint256).details: Get the whole array in `votesToProposalIds` for a given votes amount.

getRankIndex(uint256).details: Get the idx of sortedRanks considered to hold the queried rank taking deleted proposals into account.      A rank has to have > 0 votes to be considered valid.

hashComment((address,uint256,uint256,str.details: Hashing function used to build the comment id from the comment details.

isOrIsBelowTiedRank(uint256).details: Returns whether a given index in sortedRanks is tied or is below a tied rank.

proposalAddressVotes(uint256,address).details: Accessor to how many votes an address has cast for a given proposal.

proposalAddressesHaveVoted(uint256).details: Accessor to which addresses have cast a vote for a given proposal.

proposalVotes(uint256).details: Accessor to the internal vote counts for a given proposal.

setOfficialRewardsModule(address).details: Get the official rewards module contract for this contest (effectively reverse record).

totalVotesCastIsZero().details: Returns true if totalVotesCast is zero.

validateProposalData((address,bool,strin.details: Confirms that all of the metadata in the proposal is valid.

verifyProposer().details: Verifies that `account` is permissioned to propose.

voteStart().details: Timestamp the contest vote begins. Votes open at the end of this block, so it is possible to propose during this block.
